天从影响社会这个更大的层面来看，个体的、商业的力量还是太小。 「今年，我没有心思再给员工画饼了」：40 岁公司老总吐露心声 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-770c64d7faa5947d2feb6eec15e32248_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/592535554"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItYP7x8WMldwmEAMaCDkzOTU2Mjk3IIeBj6EGMCI4hAhAL3IJNTkyNTM1NTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1680488686.2453797", "card_id": "Q_359740428", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 5635}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你的导师对你说过什么让你至今难以忘怀的话？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "你的大学老师，硕士导师或者博士导师对你说过什么让你到现在还记得的话！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9123343f48b5b7ac04df2a9d60c2e870_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/359740428"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItYP7x8WMldwmEAMaCDQyMjIwODY0ILigre8FMBY4zeYCQDByCTM1OTc0MDQyOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1680488686.2460017", "card_id": "Q_593338107", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 459}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你认为学历重要还是能力更重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5038b1711c03d4f6cd8375fafffa175d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593338107"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItYP7x8WMldwmEAMaCDk0MTM0NTgwIKy6pKEGMAg4hgRAMXIJNTkzMzM4MTA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous